<abstract>
<para>
Kgpg is a simple graphical interface for gpg <ulink
url="http://gnupg.org"> (http://gnupg.org)</ulink>. Basically, It allows you to encrypt and decrypt files or messages, and to manage your keys.
</para>
</abstract>

